App.js: Sets up routes, including a fallback route for unmatched paths.

Navbar.js: Provides navigation links to the Home and About pages.

Loader.js: Displays a loading spinner while data is being fetched.

Home.js: Contains the search functionality and calls the Open Library API.

BookCard.js: Displays individual book information.

NotFound.js: Displays a 404 message when a route isnâ€™t found.

